---
description: Regarding colors, adhere to Streamlit's default color theme.
globs: ["**/*.css", "**/*.py"]
alwaysApply: true
---

Use only four colors: BG color(#000000), text color(#e7e9ea), BG sub-color(#181818), and accent color(#1d9bf0).
Do not use emojis or similar characters under any circumstances.
The base style should be monochrome.
